{"tid":1402590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚明顯有人帶風向咁屌前線","createTime":"2019-08-03T16:34:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:44:30.000Z","uid":96704,"like":137,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"66b8ecfd06c3225188c2cfc3392783c713c1048f","tid":1402590,"uid":96704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:34:04.000Z","msg":"推一萬步嚟講前線就算真係錯撚晒，你最多話佢哋天真錯判形勢<br />\n個個有心人嘅post一嚟就用&quot;抵死&quot;依兩隻咁極端嘅字字明顯係想帶風向激起大家對前線嘅敵意<br />\n我信唔少人（包括我）睇完都就住當時嘅情況比佢影響到<br />\n希望大家冷靜落嚟再諗下，切忌中計<br />\n抗爭嘅路仲係好長<br />\n希望前線同和理非好似兩夫婦咁床頭打交床尾和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不分化，不割蓆，be water, 5/8罷"},{"pid":"08499e68866015956c88dbb81f944152711ee424","tid":1402590,"uid":241244,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:35:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"530bd8018e77785bce3ea68ff25fe1964ef5a0f5","tid":1402590,"uid":269280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:37:31.000Z","msg":"不割席，不篤灰，兄弟爬山各自努力！"},{"pid":"21c8a12764683da2b4a30eeee086ee1e55e64b43","tid":1402590,"uid":96704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"997919806c7dc625797c4ab5f7000eb7d3761392","tid":1402590,"uid":45523,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:41:55.000Z","msg":"其實你應該諗下係睇到心痛"},{"pid":"a997993606b2ffda15a77de6ea1294eacc6fd35d","tid":1402590,"uid":38548,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"997919806c7dc625797c4ab5f7000eb7d3761392","tid":1402590,"uid":45523,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"