msg":"其實上兩個禮拜連登都係咁，唔排除有堆混水摸魚嘅AC/一毛"},{"pid":"d3773a5bf00ba0ae331ab3b2c9ebdffd06e81c94","tid":1402590,"uid":61334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:46:01.000Z","msg":"我冇野講<br />\n我要搵律師"},{"pid":"fa07159ddb25d7f2d06c367ba9fcadfe6c9f8bb8","tid":1402590,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:46:28.000Z","msg":"不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求"},{"pid":"d695378d05bb906a6b0fc6c768cd58d0f0b421bb","tid":1402590,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:47:16.000Z","msg":"小心3毛帶風向<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G8sKaYC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG8sKaYC.png&h=b0564f77&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42f9b1d03b5872e4d4df550d421bd86f710182da","tid":1402590,"uid":157413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:48:59.000Z","msg":"唔理班三毛五毛點撚樣分化點樣鬧前線都好，我絕對唔會對任何前線割席同指責"},{"pid":"5529e5c23bea87bf6c19ded897977fa643d24dc6","tid":1402590,"uid":53537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:50:17.000Z","msg":"一定要推"},{"pid":"be9ff374c2e752ac9ff85e9523a0580d5317887a","tid":1402590,"uid":55874,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:50:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">sorry廣傳返</span><br />\n<br />\n正確做法︰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0VMCvYY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0VMCvYY.png&h=a4333331&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1. 周圍暢通無阻叫「通」形地。係每次行動一開始嘅時候，呢個係前線打狗最佳時機，狗得一隊，而我方人數最多，呢個時候係最有機會打嬴嘅時候，因為狗無槍、無速龍，仲會除低面罩休息，佢地睇死我地唔敢攻！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gDLjKi3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgDLjKi3.png&h=a6cdc9e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. 三面被圍叫「圍地」。係每次入夜後嘅情況，狗隻開始推進清場。呢個時候係要全速撤退，唔係死守，因為最佳進攻時機已經過咗！等人地上晒裝，增援晒先打，唔好咁傻！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ipADfqP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FipADfqP.png&h=130c71be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3. 四面被圍叫「死地」。呢個情況只有兩個選擇︰一，拼死殺出血路，成功率極低。二，投降。並唔存在撤退，你有路退咩？ 等呢個時候先退，係愚蠢！<br />\n<br />\n總之要打就一開始打，唔打就守到入夜就走，就係咁簡單！<br />\n<br />\n生地要攻，圍地要撤，死地要拼！<br />\n<br />\n我嘅目的係救人，唔係送頭！不服來辯！"},{"pid":"631b7a5f8d3a7df0914ee256ce4dea0dae0d0f13","tid":1402590,"uid":278168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:50:57.000Z","msg":"呢個post必須推"},{"pid":"e2ce92f37ad6060a64ddf5427a5150a04a9ba9ce","tid":1402590,"uid":273803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:51:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2aa2ae24594e82d1eb3ac10c4fb4d0f0b98c30b0","tid":1402590,"uid":289618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:55:07.000Z","msg":"我都發現到&quot;風向&quot;<br />\n星期一晚開始突然吹風向，當日極多討論小朋友無飯食，無錢買裝<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係突然間極多<br />\n<br />\n然後今日&quot;風向&quot;吊前線<br />\n<br />\n和理非有auntie 係防暴前講過道理、有人拎過花高舉雙手走近、有伯伯企係防暴前面，佢地最後得到防暴乜野對待全部人有目共睹。<br />\n吊前線之前，和理非認為有更好既方法就去做！覺得唔忍心佢地送頭就落場拉佢地走，唔係係度吹&quot;風向&quot;"},{"pid":"809b061f2c3bdac07e63936327d7692b93854cfe","tid":1402590,"uid":96704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:56:07.000Z","msg":"唉連仔個延遲評分系統早啲出今日都唔使搞到風向帶得咁犀利<br />\n希望大家暫時推上去黃大仙啲po洗走啲屌人po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80287ad0d4e1b926545fcfaef1249af465f1556","tid":1402590,"uid":272968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:02:53.000Z","msg":"全部block哂去"},{"pid":"ed29b5a7093327cb3faed055fd6b93a3ad69f40e","tid":1402590,"uid":71140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:07:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"947941c4de8c3a1b359db9401c82643b6becbe83","tid":1402590,"uid":96704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:10:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1402388/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1402388/page/1</a><br />\n推！絕對唔係抵撚死"},{"pid":"b6166a0e4ea9136344602978cfd8cb903296def6","tid":1402590,"uid":38164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a997993606b2ffda15a77de6ea1294eacc6fd35d","tid":1402590,"uid":38548,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"997919806c7dc625797c4ab5f7000eb7d3761392","tid":1402590,"uid":45523,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:41:55.000Z","msg":"其實你應該諗下係睇到心痛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:43:02.000Z","msg":"心痛會覺得佢地抵死嗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:15:46.000Z","msg":"只係一個po咁講，唔應該係屌前線<br />\nps我都有叫人be water"},{"pid":"c8cca3171930bf5e348d3e0be1088d70689cb6fa","tid":1402590,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:17:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">覺得今晚黃大仙街坊<br />\n好似一下子團結返全部香港人</span></span>"},{"pid":"fc290a8567462cd18cff8e44c8e2259de1bac79b","tid":1402590,"uid":79974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:19:26.000Z","msg":"不捉鬼，不指責，只解決問題"},{"pid":"6cc4f7690a67c3c1b1593e07c75698847b2ad059","tid":1402590,"uid":80015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:33:18.000Z","msg":"多謝前線   <br />\n8月5日我會罷工"},{"pid":"81da985ae6d007f759d4c8c64a3349deefbec518","tid":1402590,"uid":158889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:34:15.000Z","msg":"明顯有五毛帶撚哂風向 網上戰線都比人打撚散哂仲叫自己冷氣軍師 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e5eb236d005e470a58aef3f40b6812fc658f7d","tid":1402590,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:34:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3133991fa263a67724ae8dd392c0c0578eb8f1f2","tid":1402590,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:07:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"34862140462bf8dde5acbaa3c8c8722a7fbc488e","tid":1402590,"uid":173849,"